{"tid":1871157,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］ 還息唔還本 ＝ 債務重組 ＝破產前管理","createTime":"2020-02-09T09:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T08:07:40.000Z","uid":338879,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8744de98b121b722bd7717a85b85c361aa9501dd","tid":1871157,"uid":338879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"依家間間大行都推還息唔還本<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">好聽啲就叫債務重組，唔好聽根本就係企業/個人破產前管理</span><br />\n<br />\n如果借錢個間公司/個人本身有能力，點會比幾個月瘟疫就拖死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家銀行錢就借曬出去，但就收唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，銀行唔想條數變bad debt 就唯有懶好聽咁restructuring 啲貸款，咁就可以報財披時冇咁拖死個營利，但實際上現金流就收少左<br />\n<br />\n個市拖得一時唔拖得一世，中國同香港經濟已收皮，等睇支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝 天滅中共！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎：滙豐加推措施助企業紓困  涉資逾300億元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200209/bkn-20200209151947746-0209_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200209%2Fbkn-20200209151947746-0209_00842_001.html&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqk%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=47944000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200209/bkn-20200209151947746-0209_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8a00bca1477a4882562a4f7d9bdb2dfd2c41e8f4","tid":1871157,"uid":338879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:42:02.000Z","msg":"推下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b7b8cb825177e97393f56e3787f87436ecfd2b","tid":1871157,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"唱定USD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577032e9a22762daf646c15f8ff0e089244f36dd","tid":1871157,"uid":338879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51b7b8cb825177e97393f56e3787f87436ecfd2b","tid":187